rows.label: qst202511_0010
rows.name: They seem to be having fun.

rows.label: qst202511_0030
rows.name:
Looking at them like this, those
two make a pretty good team.

rows.label: qst202511_0050
rows.name:
That's strange... I thought
I'd find it here...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202511_0080
rows.name:
If you tell me what you
are looking for, I can
conduct a search as well.

rows.label: qst202511_0090
rows.name:
It would increase
efficiency, would it not?

rows.label: qst202511_0100
rows.name:
That's true, but...
[ML:Dash ]it's still a secret.

rows.label: qst202511_0200
rows.name:
Don't be reckless, KOS-MOS
Re:! What if you got hurt?

rows.label: qst202511_0210
rows.name:
No...[ML:Dash ] There is no need
to worry about me.

rows.label: qst202511_0220
rows.name:
More importantly, for a short
while, please hide behind me.

rows.label: qst202511_0240
rows.name:
Don't get hurt, KOS-MOS Re:, but
don't you dare lose, either.

rows.label: qst202511_0250
rows.name:
I sense a contradiction in your
instructions, but acknowledged.

rows.label: qst202511_0260
rows.name:
Altering mission priority.
Astelle's instructions will
now be top priority.
